，在台湾问题上不断歪曲和掏空一个中国政策，发表不负责任言论的正是美方。美方最近开始强调要维护每一个国家的主权和领土完整，希望美方首先在台湾问题上言行一致，不要搞双重标准。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2153ef3b1b7e7926d5c5536228a59536_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/546528914"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIj5nb4saBr/0jEAMaCDgzNzMzOTgwIMCwopcGMAA49AVAIHIJNTQ2NTI4OTE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1659488088.6327028", "card_id": "Q_545817668", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 84}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么在欧美爆火的电助力自行车 e-bike 在国内市场却鲜有人问津？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是产品不符合国内需求还是哪些原因......"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/545817668"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij5nb4saBr/0jEAMaCDgzNTc1Nzg2IIr6iZcGMAA4jQJAIXIJNTQ1ODE3NjY4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1659488088.6335452", "card_id": "Q_393810993", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何巧妙的刻画网络小说中人物的形象？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3079f9db68603c384e96fe4b2dc42972_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/393810993"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij5nb4saBr/0jEAMaCDQ5NzkyNDM3IMKF3PUFMAA4xwFAInIJMzkzODEwOTkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1659488088.634025", "card_id": "Q_546439918", "feed_spec